  "remarks": "TAe.013 Rahat Ltd. Was used by Taliban leadership to transfer funds originating from external donors and narcotics trafficking to finance Taliban activity as of 2011 and 2012. Owned by Mohammed Qasim Sadozai Khudai Rahim (TI.Q.165.12.). Also associated Mohammad Naim Barich Khudaidad (TI.N.13.01.).; Listing: Listed on 21 November 2012 (amended 27 Jun. 2013)",
